OL,6,CG1976FAngela Rippon is the first
OL,7,Fmember of the BBC TV news presenting
OL,8,Fteam to front the new look BBC One news
OL,9,Fprogrammes. One presenter would now
OL,10,Fread each of the main BBC One news
OL,11,Fprogrammes each weekday - Midday News,
OL,12,FEvening News and the Nine o'Clock News.
OL,13,
OL,14,CG1987FSue Lawley presents the BBC One
OL,15,Fweekend news for the first time, due to
OL,16,Fthe ferry disaster at Zeebrugge.
